  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4 \u0dbd\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dda \u0da9\u0dd3\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d87\u0daf\u0dca\u0daf \u0dc3\u0dc4\u0dba\u0d9a \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd6",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Helper Mattoo pulled diesel in the garbage truck",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Wadduwa police said that an employee of the Panadura local council was arrested for stealing 20 liters of diesel from the lorry transporting garbage at night.",
        "The police said that the arrested was an employee working as an assistant in the JCB machine of the Panadura local council.",
        "After informing the Wadduwa police that two employees working in the council were stealing 20 liters of diesel from the lorry parked in the vehicle yard last night on the 24th, the police said that one of the suspects was arrested and the hidden 20 liters of diesel was found.",
        "A senior police officer said that action will be taken to arrest the other suspect involved in the incident.",
        "For the past few days, the Panadura local council was in dire straits without fuel to transport the garbage, a senior official said."
      ],
